		{"id":"cdc4697c47f04101","type":"text","text":"SetBuilderFunc","x":476,"y":847,"width":169,"height":73},
		{"id":"7600781ccaa92087","type":"text","text":"在`ProgressPattern`类中动态创建一个`FrameNode`对象。首先，它检查`makeFunc_`是否已存在。如果不存在，则返回`nullptr`。接着，它获取`ProgressPaintProperty`的值，并将其与`maxValue`相比较。然后，它获取`EventHub`，并检查它是否为`nullptr`。如果检查通过，则调用`makeFunc_`的值，并传入`ProgressConfiguration`对象。\nreturn (makeFunc_.value())(ProgressConfiguration{value, total, enabled});\n主要作用就是创建了一个FrameNode对象","x":1296,"y":644,"width":531,"height":240,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"80464d8bdab84d4b","type":"text","text":"BuildContentModifierNode","x":1076,"y":644,"width":160,"height":77},
		{"id":"887b769a14be36b7","type":"text","text":"makeFunc_ = std::move(makeFunc)","x":756,"y":860,"width":250,"height":60,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"17fc85c3f59846ab","type":"text","text":"FireBuilder()//创建一个FrameNode对象\ncontentModifierNode_ = BuildContentModifierNode();\nhost->AddChild(contentModifierNode_, 0);//添加子节点\nhost->MarkNeedFrameFlushDirty(PROPERTY_UPDATE_MEASURE); //标脏","x":603,"y":604,"width":403,"height":213},
		{"id":"4b5e6e9c7c608733","type":"text","text":"setContentModifierBuilder","x":903,"y":-415,"width":168,"height":53},
		{"id":"577bcb4c803ae9c6","type":"text","text":"this.builder = modifier.applyContent();\n把自定义的builder拿出来\nthis.modifier = modifier","x":1160,"y":-480,"width":284,"height":109},
		{"id":"33cff0c95ddfe654","type":"text","text":"nativePtr progress framenode指针","x":1160,"y":-371,"width":210,"height":53},
		{"id":"344107194da874db","type":"text","text":"**makeFunc**是一个JS类型对象，jsObject中存在一个名为makeContentModifierNode的函数，那么makeFunc将指向该函数。否则makeFunc指向nullptr\n\n首先，它从`jsObject`中获取一个名为\"makeContentModifierNode\"的方法，然后检查这个方法是否是一个函数。如果不是函数，则返回`nullptr`。如果是函数，则将该函数赋值给`func`变量。最后，调用`func`变量，并传入`jsObject`、`params`和函数的参数数量，传给定义的变量result","x":1444,"y":-318,"width":455,"height":266,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"b18b9b2eb1548d33","type":"text","text":"从result结果中获取一个`FrameNode`对象，并检查它是否为`nullptr`。如果检查通过，则返回该`FrameNode`的引用。","x":1113,"y":-260,"width":242,"height":151},
		{"id":"6b9b980266e2cdf7","type":"text","text":"setContentModifierBuilder","x":936,"y":429,"width":182,"height":57},
		{"id":"077ad9213d6c599d","type":"text","text":"方法指针具体方法：`keysOfProgress`数组中的每个字符串分别是`\"value\"`、`\"total\"`和`\"enabled\"`，而`valuesOfProgress`数组中的每个`JSValueRef`对象分别是通过`panda::NumberRef::New`和`panda::BooleanRef::New`方法创建的，分别用于表示配置中的`value_`、`total_`和`enabled_`成员变量。","x":1128,"y":117,"width":336,"height":248},
		{"id":"6abf41f564e0ff3f","type":"text","text":"两个指针：一个是framenode。另一个是ArkProgressComponent指针","x":1156,"y":418,"width":280,"height":80},
		{"id":"cf458214e519f673","type":"text","text":"`params`数组中的每个`panda::JSValueRef`对象分别是通过`context`和`progress`参数传递的","x":1175,"y":-60,"width":242,"height":125},
		{"id":"e26dc608394d2e47","type":"text","text":"setContentModifier(modifier);","x":676,"y":429,"width":182,"height":57},
		{"id":"6ceb4ffdecc084d2","type":"text","text":"return this.progressNode.getFrameNode();获得节点","x":697,"y":35,"width":263,"height":117,"color":"1"},
		{"id":"d0dc960964551fe2","type":"text","text":"return new ArkProgressComponent(nativeNode);\n","x":697,"y":192,"width":260,"height":97,"color":"1"},
